			<div class="content" id="post-content-1450101">
									

<p>Class D termination is becoming 682 chow. I had originally considered allowing both &quot;they're killed&quot; and &quot;they're mind-wiped and cycled back into the system&quot; as my headcanon, but this&#8230; this replaces both of them.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">Maybe this is why 682 doesn't breach containment as often as you think it'd want to. We give it what it wants (to snack on humans) once a month, and it's happy, or at least not as mad.</span> In retrospect, this idea is stupid. Still liked the story.</p>

